Summaries

three sample summaries

[1] The speaker insists that the existing system of white supremacy can be changed through our actions. Many incidents in which innocent black people are arrested by the police and killed in the worst cases have been occurring frequently in America for a long time. He created a game to help understand these white people's supremacist incidents.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                               
[2] This speech talked about discrimination between blacks and whites. In his speech, he brought up the news of a police officer shooting and killing an unarmed man in 2018. A variety of other issues were covered, such as a black woman who was just standing there being reported to the police by a white person. It is true that the problem of discrimination against black people is still widespread, and that there is also a thing called whiteism. He also says that in order to change these societies, we have to change the system that everyone thinks about.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                           
[3] Speaker has an extraordinary name by his mother. She told her son about this world with black’s history and martial arts. Sidwell, where he studied science, was a good place to learn science and art, but the art of living amongst whiteness. America taught him what it means to be black in the US. When he was driving, he was stopped by the police without violating the rules. At that time his head was full of bad events which happened recently. After that, he started looking for nearby events. He is referring to a system of structural advantage that favors white people over others in social, economic and political arenas. When he saw the accident repeated, he got angry and was also inspired to create a game. It is a game of words that would allow people to transform this traumatic exposure into more of a healing experience. The game has 4 levels. First level is to reverse the roles. Second level is to increase the believability of reversal. Third level is to change the action. Lastly, there is bonus level. Speaker says white people too easily call on deadly force to secure their comfort. So, people need to think about the game. He says there is a structure to systemic abuses of power. We are able to change stories about black and white.
